{\*\cs47\fs20\b0\i\expnd-1\expndtw-4 movement accuracy,}{\fs20\expnd-1\expndtw-4  which decreases when tactile information is not available, especially at the fingertips. Research has demonstrated poorer accuracy when tactile feedback is removed or minimized for several skills including pointing (Rao & \line }
